Author: Hell-raiser

Body: Hi,  I've seen the Sberbank logo on your site and you mentioned your partnership with 150 businesses. Sberbank is the biggest state-owned Russian bank, so making partners with it would give a dramatic boost to the popularity and publicity of your platform.  Could you expand more on the type of this partnership?

Author: Jammalan the Prophet
Title: [ANN][ICO][ENJL] Crypto and fiat money in one wallet!
Body: Hello! Thank you for your interest! We have already integrated a wallet into the Enjoy Life application where you can store both USD, BTC and ETH (implementation in the near future). Moreover, you have the opportunity to convert your crypto currency at any time. Our lawyers are working now in the sphere of integration of our wallet into the banking system (Visa&Mastercard), as well as on a clear work scheme based on the legal financial company, Enjoy Life.  For today, we are negotiating and almost completely worked out a scheme of integrating our business to Russia and will begin to work fully in Russia from January-February. Right now, you are not supposed to have any problems working with USD and BTC in Enjoy Life, regardless the country where are you from. Hope, this information was beneficial to you!

Author: Jammalan the Prophet
Title: [ANN][ICO][ENJL] Crypto and fiat money in one wallet!
Body: Hello! Thank you very much for your interest! Regarding the picture that is placed in the Enjoy Life Whitepaper, this one was taken during the International Blochain Forum in Moscow, where Enjoy Life was an official partner of the event, in line with Sberbank and the others.You can find an article talking about this event here: https://medium.com/@enjoy_life_app/international-blockchain-forum-and-thats-not-the-end-c3b48f2128ee  At the moment, we are not partnering with Sberbank, however among our official partners are Auchan hypermarkets and more than 150 of others. If you are interested in who are the partners of Enjoy life, you can take a look in the app, they are fully described there. All the partners have special priorities working with Enjoy Life, as the clients do. Please, read our Whitepaper to learn more about the terms for partnership and how you can benefit even more with the ENJL tokens.

Author: Jammalan the Prophet
Title: [ANN][ICO][ENJL] Crypto and fiat money in one wallet!
Body: Thank you for your comment, we really appreciate it! Regarding your first question: as for now, we have not announced yet a mobile wallet compatible with Windows OS, however, it does not mean we will not consider it. We have emphasised on IOS and Andriod development to make it amazing and efficient. Regarding your second question: Our developers have already released a beta version in English that is on the final stage of being officially released(For now, there is already a Russian version that is available). At the same time, we are translating the app to other languages, so that when we announce it officially- they will come up at the same time. But no worries- we won't take long with it, so stay tuned!
